package pages

// siteLogo is the "{ gsx } ui" wordmark, inlined so the header paints it with
// no extra request and no theme flash. The two fills ride CSS custom
// properties (--site-logo-strong/--site-logo-muted, defined in web/site.css)
// that flip under .dark to the dark-variant brand colors, so one SVG serves
// both themes. Source of truth: the design set in the repo history
// (gsxui-logo.svg / gsxui-logo-dark.svg); regenerate by re-inlining if the
// wordmark is redesigned.
